      "text": " In order to proceed, it is necessary to express the term  $[Z_2]$  in terms of the tautological line bundle  $\\zeta$  of  $\\mathbb{P}(E_{\\mathcal{L}})$  and  $\\pi^*\\beta$ , where  $\\beta$  is a divisor on  $X^{[2]}$  (cf. Fulton 2013, Chapter 3.3). This is achieved by calculating the first Chern class of  $E_{\\mathcal{L}}$  in proposition 3.1.",
